# Project Overview

This project supports the Forge2gether Essay Contest Phase 1 system.

The system uses:
- Google Forms for intake
- Google Sheets as operational database
- Google Apps Script for automation
- Next.js static/lightweight website for public pages

Do not overbuild.
Do not add full user accounts unless explicitly requested.
Do not add Supabase or a database in Phase 1.
Optimize for fewer than 500 students.
Prioritize simplicity, reliability, and clean handoff to nontechnical admins.
